These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
House: wooden, farmhouse, tower, cottage
4 different games are played: chess, poker, mah-jongg, go
1. the person playing chess is somewhere to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##5
2. the farmhouse house is not the person playing chess##6
3. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing go##1
4. the tower house is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the wooden house is on the right of the person playing chess##1
6. the person playing chess is not the tower house##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | farmhouse   | cottage    | wooden    | tower |
| Sport      | go | chess | mah-jongg | poker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
City: prague, edinburgh, colone, paris
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, april, june, january
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to colone##5
3. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to paris##5
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is not the person who's birthday is in april##6
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
7. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
8. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | edinburgh  | colone    | prague | paris    |
| Food       | january | april | june  | august |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, april, september, january
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, british, dutch, chinese
1. the person who's birthday is in january is not the colombian##6
2. the british is not the person who's birthday is in september##6
3. the dutch is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
4. the british is the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the british##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4
7. the colombian is on the far left or far right##3
8. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | january       | april  | june  | september |
| Job        | dutch | chinese | british | colombian  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, project-manager, journalist, dancer
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, filmmaking, writing, camping
1. the journalist is on the left of the dancer##1
2. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
3. the person who's hobby is camping is not the project-manager##6
4. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
6. the dancer is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | project-manager | journalist | dancer     | firefighter |
| Transport   | filmmaking     | writing    | hiking | camping    |

