.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, argentine, egyptian, colombian
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, may, february, september
1. the russian is on the left of the colombian##1
2. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
3. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
4. the argentine is not the person who's birthday is in september##6
5. the person who's birthday is in april is not the russian##6
6. the egyptian is on the left of the argentine##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | russian        | colombian | egyptian | argentine |
| Transport   | september | april | may     | february   |

