.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, fanta, tea, cola
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, skiing, basketball, climbing
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking cola is not the person who's sport is skiing##6
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
5. the person drinking tea is the person drinking tea##1
6. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5
7. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
8. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5
9. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | fanta | tea    | sprite  | cola   |
| Nationality   | basketball  | climbing | skiing | swimming |

