.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, poppy, amaryllis, begonia
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, april, december, january
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
2. the person who's birthday is in december is not the person who growspoppy##6
3. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
6. the person who growspoppy is the person who's birthday is in october##1
7. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | begonia | poppy     | amaryllis | daffodil |
| Music-Genre   | december | october | january      | april         |

