.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, video-games, reading
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, february, july, march
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
7. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the person who's birthday is in march##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | rock-climbing  | fishing        | video-games      | reading          |
| Job        | may | february | march | july |

