.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
4 different games are played: bridge, scrabble, monopoly, canasta
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
1. the person playing bridge is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking mirinda is not the person playing canasta##6
3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is the person playing monopoly##1
7. the person playing bridge is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
8. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | bridge  | monopoly | canasta    | scrabble |
| Transport   | mirinda | almond-milk | hot-chocolate | iced-tea  |

