.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, apricot, black, chestnut
City: london, prague, hannover, venice
1. the person traveling to london is not the person who likes turquise##6
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
3. the person traveling to venice is the person traveling to venice##1
4. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
5. the person who likes black is not the person traveling to venice##6
6. the person traveling to prague is not the person who likes apricot##6
7. the person traveling to venice is in an even position##4
8. the person who likes black is the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | black | turquise        | chestnut  | apricot     |
| Sport   | london     | venice | prague | hannover |

