.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, cola, mirinda, fanta
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, aquamarine, red, yellow
1. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
3. the person who likes red is not the person drinking mirinda##6
4. the person drinking cola is between the person who likes yellow and the person drinking mirinda##2
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
6. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person who likes apricot and the person drinking water##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | mirinda | cola    | water | fanta |
| Music-Genre   | apricot         | aquamarine | yellow   | red     |

