.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, snake, goat, mouse
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, scientific, time-travel, fantasy
1. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##5
2. the owner of the mouse is not the person watching disaster movies##6
3. the person watching scientific movies is the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is not the owner of the mouse##6
6. the owner of the snake is not the person watching disaster movies##6
7. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | chinchilla  | goat | snake | mouse |
| Transport   | time-travel | disaster     | fantasy     | scientific    |

