4. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
5. the fonseca-smoker is between the cain-smoker and the person who's sport is soccer##2
6. the cain-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | blend | cain      | fonseca | montecristo   |
| Movie-Genre   | volleyball     | sailing | baseball   | soccer |

