5. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
6. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | colonial | futuristic | townhouse      | farmhouse   |
